      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "盛り上がった障害物競走もいよいよ大詰めだ\nゴール目前で、怜はトップと僅差の二位……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The thrilling obstacle race is reaching its climax.\nRei is currently in second place‚ trailing closely behind the leader…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.4333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2933.3333333,
          "startTime": 3.7333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-multi-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1333.3333332999998,
          "startTime": 2.1333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6416.666666699999,
          "startTime": 10.85
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-multi-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4866.666666700001,
          "startTime": 9.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "だが先頭との距離が縮まらない……！\nこのままじゃ逆転は難しいぞ、頑張れ怜！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But she's not closing the gap with the front-runner…!\nIt'll be difficult to turn the tables like this. Hang in there‚ Rei!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5400,
          "startTime": 16.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁはぁ……次が最後の障害……！\n最後は、借り物競走……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huff huff… The next obstacle…!\nThe final challenge is the borrowing stuff race…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.5666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8278.187489499998,
          "startTime": 33.8448541562
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "カードをめくって書いてある物を持ってゴールへ……\n私のカードは……えっ！？　これは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have to hold what the card is written and reach the finish line…!\nMy card is… Huh!? This is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "怜のやつ、立ち止まって何を探しているんだ？\nあ、走り出した。こっちに向かって来て……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is Rei doing‚ stopping like that?\nAh‚ she started running. She's coming this way…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2299.9999999999973,
          "startTime": 47.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！　私と一緒に来て下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san! Please come with me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "俺が！？　カードにはなんて書いてあったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me!? What did the card say?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "『頼りになる人』です！　だから私と来て下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It says \"Someone to lean on\"! That's why I want you to come with me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それで俺の所に……\nよし、行こう！　絶対一位を取るぞ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you came to me…\nAlright‚ let's go! We'll definitely take first place!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "はい！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――障害物競走終了後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After the race",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "久しぶりの全力疾走はキツかったな……\nでも、最後に逆転出来て良かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was tough running at full speed after a long time…\nBut I'm glad we were able to come from behind at the end.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "おかげで一位になれました\nありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to you‚ I was able to take first place.\nThank you very much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、怜が俺を頼りになる人だと\n思ってくれていたとはね。嬉しいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ it's nice to know that you think of me\nas a reliable person. It makes me happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "からかわないで下さい……。とっさに顔が\n思い浮かんだんだから仕方ないじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don't tease me… It was just a quick thought\nthat came to my mind‚ so it can't be helped‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……\nそれで、もう大丈夫なのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hahaha…\nSo‚ are you okay now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　何がですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "だから、衣装を着て人前に出ても平気になったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I mean‚ are you fine wearing the outfit and appearing in front of people?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そういえばそうでした……\n勝負に夢中ですっかり忘れてました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ now that you mention it…\nI completely forgot about it because I was focused on the race.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "朝からずっと緊張してたのに、レースが始まったら\n集中してて視線も気になりませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was nervous all morning‚ but once the race started‚\nI was so concentrated that I didn't even care about the gaze.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "最初の一歩を踏み出すのは勇気がいるが\n思い切って飛び込んでみれば意外と出来たりするものさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Taking the first step requires courage‚\nbut once you take the plunge‚ you'll be surprised at what you can do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね\n今はあんなに恥ずかしかったのが不思議なくらいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true.\nIt's strange how something that was so embarrassing is not a big deal anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_03-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "……もうすぐサニピの出番です\n私達の新衣装もステージも、見ていて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Our turn for Sunny Peace is coming up soon.\nPlease watch our new outfits and stage!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.5333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8200.000000000016,
