      "text": "水着みたいでちょっと恥ずかしいけど……\n夏のビーチでいつもより大胆になってしまいそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They're a bit like swimsuits‚ so it's a little embarrassing…\nI feel like I'll become more daring than usual at the summer beach.",
        "id": ""
